{
  "text": "\u2022 Pair-copula densities are estimated by the local-likelihood estimator of [CITATION_1] with quadratic polynomials. We follow the approach proposed in this paper and select nearest-neighbor bandwidths via leastsquares cross-validation. Furthermore, we adjust the selected bandwidths by the rule-of-thumb given in Section 5.3.",
